text: Shandong Experimental High School (abbreviation: SEHS, Chinese: 山东省实验中学) is a provincial key high school, in Jinan, Shandong Province, PRC. It was founded in 1948 and has been enjoying great reputation since then. It has 500 teachers and 5,700 students in 2022.《学校简介》，于2015年10月16日查阅。 == References == Category:Schools in the People's Republic of China People's Republic of China
